Good afternoon team!


Just in the process of setting up a landing page for a LifeWorks Cairns campaign for group classes, and was wondering if you know of a good solution for adding a date picker field where only certain dates are available to choose from? I found this plugin but just wanted to check if you know of a better solution. https://toroguapo.com/gf-hero/


For example if they selected Life Power would only let them pick Mondays or Wednesdays as that's the days that class runs. https://royalrehablifeworks.com.au/cairns/services/group-classes/#booking-form has an example of the form I am currently duplicating for the campaign landing page.
